{"tid":1343654,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"五金行YouTuber PVC長槍","createTime":"2019-07-21T19:10:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T06:56:52.000Z","uid":272353,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a7b376e7fbc3dae2adcc0d013b2a9c7f7cb82ea3","tid":1343654,"uid":272353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:10:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oocgw87.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Foocgw87.png&h=f3be137e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n主要材料：<br />\nPVC水管（若干條 視造型同需要    槍頭）<br />\n熱風機（將水管變型、塑型）<br />\n竹（槍身）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n道具：<br />\n電鑽<br />\n線鋸、磨砂紙（將pvc壓扁後 整個頭變矛狀）<br />\n等（唔知有冇睇漏）<br />\n<br />\n效果：<br />\n可以係厚木板（自製木盾）到留一道深坑<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同大家推薦下呢個YouTuber胡子，好有創意～<br />\n不過記住唔係簡單玩具黎架！好危險， <strong>唔好亂咁帶出街</strong><br />\n<br />\n想再簡單啲都有<br />\n口袋弓箭 Pocket shot（外國玩具自製版）<br />\n一個塑膠圓環（pvc水管/你諗到嘅固定用物品）<br />\n彈力袋（氣球）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n將氣球套上個水管到，完成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n影片實測效果：<br />\n植物果實可以打穿張靠牆嘅紙+果實爆汁<br />\n木筷 近半枝插左入個西瓜到<br />\n<br />\n留言：<br />\n以前被同學射過，流血了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好危險架，大家睇下片就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1defd61f69b1bd4b69c6f547f4a12c3d07f9ce75","tid":1343654,"uid":272353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:19:37.000Z","msg":"[img]<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/806X08E.png[/img］\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F806X08E.png%5B%2Fimg%EF%BC%BD&d=0ZQOgT4XWRiGBLzCIZSXci%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=264ba474\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/806X08E.png[/img］</a><br />\nPockets shot效果圖，手指掐住嘅前面全部入哂個西瓜<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pao3WHH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPao3WHH.png&h=f3f94f92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nPvc長矛效果 